with (at least) the following in the commit message:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    This closes #4173&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;commit 36a1188a3f9c93d21f68b591d4fd16fa90bd8bad&lt;br/&gt;
