&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-6156&quot; title=&quot;JmxReporter can&amp;#39;t handle windows style directory paths&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-6156&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-6156&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Metric tag name should not contain colons.&lt;/p&gt;

